Puppet Apply using ENC (example)
================================
https://www.example42.com/2017/04/10/environment-enforcement/

Node Classification in Hiera
============================
https://www.example42.com/2017/07/03/node-classification-options/


Hiera Version 5 Config
======================
https://puppet.com/docs/puppet/5.3/hiera_migrate.html

---
version: 5
defaults:
    datadir: data
    data_hash: yaml_data
hierarchy:
    - name: "Node Classification (ENC)"
      datadir: "enc"
      path: "nodes/%{trusted.certname}.yaml"

    - name: "V5 YAML Hierarchy"
      paths:
        - "10node/%{trusted.certname}.yaml"
        - "20cluster/%{cluster}.yaml"
        - "30datacenter/%{datacenter}.yaml"
        - "40site/%{site}.yaml"
        - "99common.yaml"

    - name: "V3 YAML Hierarchy"
      datadir: hieradata
      paths:
        - "01node/%{trusted.certname}.yaml"
        - "02cluster/%{cluster}.yaml"
        - "03datacenter/%{datacenter}.yaml"
        - "04site/%{site}.yaml"
        - "05common.yaml"


Python PIP Install
==================
curl https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py | python -

